{"tid":734503,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 私刑教育 殺你全家燒你阿媽","createTime":"2018-07-08T16:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T19:02:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38a14d4f491d821c94bd4812a66c6bcea680af93","tid":734503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ce084ad4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5837074d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=350c1cd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Equalize_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Equalize_poster.jpg&h=24b407cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4d/The_Strangers%3B_Prey_at_Night.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4d%2FThe_Strangers%253B_Prey_at_Night.jpg&h=f435c1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名為曾為政府工作的前中情局成員化名為羅柏&middot;麥考現住在麻薩諸塞州的波士頓，並在一間五金賣場上班。他協助他的同事朋友拉爾夫減重，以便通過保安考試。麥考答應已過世的妻子，絕不會再回到過去的危險生活。因妻子生前很愛看書，麥考為了達到讀滿100本書，下班後他習慣帶著一包茶包到住家附近一間餐廳看書，日復一日，過著平靜的生活..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述麥克和他的妻子辛蒂帶著他們的兒女參加了一場公路之旅，但當他們停留在一處神秘僻靜的貨櫃屋過夜時，三名蒙面精神病患者卻突然現身以滿足自己對鮮血的渴望<br />\n<br />\n12 50AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2bd907d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9de07d65\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175e55613c9ac29d1e3090457c1ec9f222cf6288","tid":734503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621765d401d97d4ac0d887000391e0f2ca6171da","tid":734503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{